hapLrt
.SH SYNOPSIS
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
HapLRT is a likelihood ratio test for haplotype lengths.
The lengths are modeled with an exponential distribution.
The sign denotes if the target has longer haplotypes (1) or the
background (-1).
